1.3
log
@Use the fancy .In macro for includes. From Jan Klemkow. ok jmc schwarze
@
text
@.\" $OpenBSD: btowc.3,v 1.2 2007/05/31 19:19:29 jmc Exp $
.\" $NetBSD: btowc.3,v 1.3 2003/04/16 13:34:40 wiz Exp $
.\"
